metadata.name: Dark Academia 1/1
metadata.description:
Sort through improbably niche inventory racks of an unpretentious collection. Precise encyclopedic organization. Entirely wearable. Sometimes crowded at noon. Royal blue letterman jacket, silver zippers, masked butterfly, locket lady and snake eyes iron on pastel patches. Metallic beaten disk earrings. 

Synth Graph: a close up center front view 21st century photograph of a beautiful female wearing high fashion streetwear, a red patchwork bomber jacket, blue crystal earrings and a nose piercing, with the busy streets of new york behind her, highly detailed. Sampler: klms, steps: 75, scale: 11.
